<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_298" id="148r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_298_r1l23">Der Stat cʒu Mecʒe </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_298_r1l24"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Vns iſt von ~ den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fürbraht worden / vvie 
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ </del> ſıch die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l26">
<del rend="strikethrough">ewr </del> cʒollner bey euch eines newen cʒolles 
<add><ab facs="#facs_298_r1l25">genant der maltat </ab></add> vnterfangen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ʒe </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l28">
<add><ab facs="#facs_298_r1l27">
<del rend="strikethrough">nemen </del></ab></add> vnd den 
<add><ab facs="#facs_298_line_1577195115351_3734">
<del rend="strikethrough">alſo </del></ab></add> von den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> nemen </del> <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd cʒenemen mainen das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l29">doch 
<del rend="strikethrough">do </del> von alter niht <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeẏ . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr mit <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l30"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> cʒollnern ſchicken vnd beſtellen wöllet / daʒ ſie die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l31">mit <expan>ſölch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>newe<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒöllen v̈nbeſwert . ſunder ſie 
<del rend="strikethrough"> bey alter </del> damit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l32">bey alter guter gewonheıt <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . laſſen . Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_298_r1l33">vvir v̈mb ewr erſamkeit vnd die ewrn gern verdienen <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_298" id="148r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Mecze</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns ist von den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fürbraht worden, wie sich die czollner
                        bey euch eines newen czolles, <add>genant der maltat</add>, unterfangen
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und den von den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und cze nemen mainen, das doch von alter
                        niht <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> sey. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir mit <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> czollnern schicken und bestellen wöllet, daz
                        sie die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>sölch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>newe<ex>n</ex></expan> czöllen ünbeswert, sunder sie damit bey alter
                        guter gewonheit <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lassen. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ümb ewr ersamkeit und die ewrn
                        gern verdienen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
